TY  - CONF
JO  - Data Engineering, 2006. ICDE '06. Proceedings of the 22nd International Conference on
TI  - Taming Compliance with Sarbanes-Oxley Internal Controls Using Database Technology
T2  - Data Engineering, 2006. ICDE '06. Proceedings of the 22nd International Conference on
IS  - 
SN  - 
VO  - 
SP  - 92
