JO  - Policies for Distributed Systems and Networks, 2006. Policy 2006. Seventh IEEE International Workshop on
TI  - Policy languages for digital identity management in federation systems
T2  - Policies for Distributed Systems and Networks, 2006. Policy 2006. Seventh IEEE International Workshop on
IS  - 
